title: ONE Distribution Presents The Infamous Mobb Deep
description:
Christmas came early for SUPRA this year as the team was treated to a live performance by The Infamous Mobb Deep at the annual holiday party amid the cheer, and the drinks, and the food, and the drinks, and the drinks. Happy Holidays to everyone from SUPRA, and a big thank you to Mobb Deep.
